column16: Cole Gillespie lines out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Justin Smoak homers (4) on a fly ball to left field.   Kyle Seager scores.
Kyle Seager doubles (6) on a line drive to left fielder Marwin Gonzalez.   Robinson Cano scores.  Kyle Seager advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by shortstop Jonathan Villar.
Adam LaRoche doubles (5) on a sharp fly ball to left fielder L.  J.   Hoes.   Jayson Werth scores.
Craig Gentry lines out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Coco Crisp pops out to second baseman Jose Altuve.
Daric Barton flies out to left fielder Alex Presley.
Craig Gentry pops out to first baseman Marc Krauss on the infield fly rule.
Dustin Ackley flies out softly to left fielder Alex Presley.
Justin Smoak homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.   Kyle Seager scores.
Jed Lowrie pops out to third baseman Matt Dominguez in foul territory.
Craig Gentry walks.   John Jaso to 3rd.    Josh Reddick to 2nd.
Josh Reddick singles on a ground ball to right fielder George Springer.   John Jaso to 2nd.
